{"tid":1964113,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"復刻天安門事件？ 美專家揭中國造假疫情3部曲","createTime":"2020-04-08T14:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T19:47:44.000Z","uid":75656,"like":80,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"70a84800e536588e480f5d1b607ed7fb02379fa1","tid":1964113,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:44:00.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎疫情愈演愈烈，中國頻以「大外宣」轉移焦點，企圖撇清疫情爆發的責任，甚至還對外聲稱抗疫有成。對此，美國國家安全分析師、IRIS獨立研究創始人雷貝卡&middot;格蘭特（Rebecca Grant）撰文揭露中國疫情造假3部曲，指北京正復刻天安門事件模式，在未來數年內，將持續向世界傳輸疫情假訊息。<br />\n<br />\n格蘭特在《福斯新聞》以「中國的冠狀病毒欺騙活動──掩蓋策略3部曲」（China's coronavirus deception campaign &ndash; three parts to their cover-up strategy）撰文批評，在這次危害全球的武漢肺炎疫情中，中國起初就隱匿疫情，接下來還計劃繼續欺騙。<br />\n<br />\n格蘭特說，中國外交部發言人華春瑩與趙立堅先後否認中國是疫情的源頭，還把矛頭指向美國，她認為，更多的謊言將只會浪費更多時間，直言華的言論只是中國展開全球攻勢的一部份，就是試圖推動「中國的英勇行動為遏止該病毒的全球傳播，並贏得了寶貴的時間」，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>他更批評，「騙」才是中國國際政治、商業與軍事戰略的核心策略。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n「中國圍繞這個病毒的欺騙分三個階段。」格蘭特指出，第一、中國從2019年11月下旬開始掩蓋武漢肺炎疫情的爆發，隱瞞病毒的性質和進展的相關消息，而武漢封城措施更是為時已晚。<br />\n<br />\n第二、中國在一月份和二月份壓低有關感染病例和死亡人數的實際數字，「這一點特別有害，因為很多美國模型都依賴中國數據，來預測武漢肺炎在美國各州的傳播，並指導公共衛生政策、關閉學校和企業。」<br />\n<br />\n「最後則是讓美國當代罪羔羊。」格蘭特說，從3月中旬起，中國擴大外宣，假消息開始流竄，先由趙立堅宣稱武漢肺炎病毒是由美軍帶來的，接著再由中國國家衛健委高級別專家組組長鍾南山「圓謊」，批美國控制不住疫情的話，將造成全球大災難。<br />\n<br />\n綜觀上述，格蘭特認為，中共正運用1949年毛澤東時期贏得國共內戰的做法，以《孫子兵法》的欺瞞、狡詐、作弊對外打宣傳戰，就像1989年天安門事件一樣，這次病毒的爆發將成為未來幾年中國假訊息的主題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3126274\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3126274&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbpwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=0da55578\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3126274&h=af5b92fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3126274</a><br />\n<br />\n Fox News:<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/opinion/coronavirus-china-deception-campaign-three-parts-rebecca-grant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fopinion%2Fcoronavirus-china-deception-campaign-three-parts-rebecca-grant&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbpwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=97b1bada\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fopinion%2Fcoronavirus-china-deception-campaign-three-parts-rebecca-grant&h=e3699e1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxnews.com/opinion/coronavirus-china-deception-campaign-three-parts-rebecca-grant</a>"},{"pid":"5dd3ba8f034d3f23bd0d6b01e33fbd7d77579807","tid":1964113,"uid":253826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d02cee6173c2be3c1d4fd90fc7804b903421b03","tid":1964113,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de853e066df5711602ae2206e00446fd2e469d3","tid":1964113,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:48:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cf1432c96f7f251bbddf24f4f8f17ee8ee341873","tid":1964113,"uid":3776,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:49:05.000Z","msg":"希望可以喚醒更多歐豬同美豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616dddc201f3dc2f9028e8e6beed944246dd811d","tid":1964113,"uid":14494,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:50:16.000Z","msg":"俄大哥都淨係敢係歐亞獨裁統治<br />\n中共傻撚到去全球播毒仲要挑美國機<img src=\"/asse